Get free standard shipping to your front door or almost anywhere when you make a $50 minimum purchase. Get Full Details

Free standard shipping is limited to locations within the continental United States and Alaska. We do not 
currently ship to Hawaii, P.O. boxes, or international addresses.
Free standard shipping applies to purchases totaling $50 or more after promotions and discounts are 
applied.
Gift cards and taxes do not qualify toward the minimum purchase requirement.
For purchases under $50 a flat rate shipping fee of $9.95 applies, except for orders shipped to a dealership which is free.
Standard shipping to APO/FPO/DPO military addresses is always free, regardless of order amount.  

FREE RETURNS
Orders of any amount can be returned for free by mail or in store, for any reason, within 45 days of the 
shipping date. Get Full 
