	Harley – Replica Saddlebag Lid Latch Hardware Kit 2014 To Present

 

 







 






$200.00


Harley Davidson Motorcycle Saddlebag Lid Hardware
Building your bike and you misplaced your hardware? Or converting your old style bike to the new HD latch kit? Whatever the reason John Shope has got you covered. Complete kit to get your lids opening and closing properly. All hardware included. Trust in the Bird.

Complete hardware kit for 2014 to present touring models.
Easy bolt on with all screws included.
Will come with chrome latches only.
Made in the USA.




 
 
